up video to talk about that in greater detail.

157
00:13:56,960 --> 00:14:00,719
Doomerism, inactivity and weaponized hopelessness  

158
00:14:00,720 --> 00:14:10,559
are the only trump cards left for the powers 
that don’t want change. Don’t let them win.

